Ninjutsu {B}{R}
[i]Hellstorm[/i] – When Yuzu, Covert Crane enters, if she wasn't cast, she deals 1 damage to each creature target player controls.
[i]Crit[/i] – Whenever Yuzu deals combat damage to a player, you may return a creature you control to its owner's hand, or create a Treasure token.
